<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /></view><text>家长服务</text></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content"><view class="hero"><text>家长服务中心</text><text>监督服务质量 · 分派处理 · 提升家长满意度</text></view><view class="metric-grid"><view class="metric-card" wx:for="{{metrics}}" wx:key="label"><text class="{{item.tone}}">●</text><view><text>{{item.label}}</text><text>{{item.value}}</text></view><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view></view><view class="tabs"><view class="tab {{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{tabs}}" wx:key="key" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="switchTab">{{item.label}}</view></view><view class="feedback-card" wx:for="{{feedbacks}}" wx:key="name"><image src="{{item.avatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="student-copy"><text>{{item.name}}　<text>学员</text></text><text>{{item.classInfo}}</text><text>班级</text></view><view class="feedback-type"><text>{{item.type}}</text><text>◷ {{item.time}}</text><text>反馈时间</text></view><view class="owner"><text>♙ {{item.owner}}</text><text>负责人</text><text class="{{item.tone}}">{{item.status}}</text></view><button bindtap="openFeedback">查看处理</button></view><view class="chart-grid"><view class="trend-card"><view><text>满意度趋势</text><text>近7天⌄</text></view><view class="line-chart"><view></view><text>86%</text></view></view><view class="category-card"><view><text>常见问题分类</text><text>近30天⌄</text></view><view class="category-row" wx:for="{{categories}}" wx:key="name"><text>{{item.name}}</text><view><view style="width: {{item.width}};"></view></view><text>{{item.value}}</text></view></view></view><view class="visit-card"><view><text>今日待回访</text><text>共 3 个 ›</text></view><view class="visit-row" wx:for="{{feedbacks}}" wx:key="name"><image src="{{item.avatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><text>{{item.name}}</text><text>{{item.classInfo}}</text><text>{{item.type}}</text><button bindtap="openFeedback">去回访</button></view></view><view class="work-tip">♢ 校区负责人工作重点：监督服务质量，分派处理反馈，跟进解决进度，提升家长满意度。</view><view class="safe-space"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
